name: visor
full_description:
[VISOR](https://github.com/davidebolo1993/VISOR) is available as a [Docker image](https://hub.docker.com/r/davidebolo1993/visor). One can pull the VISOR image using:

`docker pull davidebolo1993/visor`

Then run:

`docker run davidebolo1993/visor VISOR --help`

An interactive tty to the docker container can be run using:

`docker run -ti davidebolo1993/visor`

`$(visorenv) VISOR --help`
